WEBVTT

01:37.580 --> 01:40.650
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.250 --> 01:43.550
[Episode 9]

01:45.150 --> 01:46.280
Master, be careful.

01:54.000 --> 01:55.330
Master, let me help you.

01:55.640 --> 01:58.100
You call this place...
Nine Absolutes Cave?

02:02.120 --> 02:02.710
Master.

02:03.790 --> 02:04.350
Master.

02:04.350 --> 02:06.610
Don't you have the incredibly powerful,

02:06.790 --> 02:07.710
always battle-ready,

02:07.710 --> 02:09.710
divine weapon Nine Absolutes Sword?

02:09.710 --> 02:11.240
I just borrowed the name

02:11.430 --> 02:14.030
and called this place
the Nine Absolutes Cave.

02:14.280 --> 02:15.340
Isn't it majestic?

02:17.960 --> 02:19.690
You're living a good life here.

02:20.840 --> 02:22.520
Where is the Immortality Pill?

02:22.520 --> 02:23.450
It's over there.

02:23.470 --> 02:25.000
It's still brewing though.

02:29.900 --> 02:30.990
It's cold

02:31.079 --> 02:32.410
and chilly in this cave.

02:33.079 --> 02:35.140
I rely on this furnace to warm my quilt

02:35.360 --> 02:36.620
to help me fall asleep.

02:42.430 --> 02:43.890
Come over and have a drink.

02:44.470 --> 02:46.590
This is a sixty-year-old Luosang wine.

02:46.590 --> 02:48.400
We buried it together back then.

02:49.470 --> 02:51.200
I just took it out a few days ago.

02:51.910 --> 02:53.240
Such good Luosang wine!

02:53.360 --> 02:54.560
I must have a few sips.

02:57.190 --> 02:57.870
Come.

02:58.470 --> 02:59.680
Lu, come sit.

03:02.960 --> 03:03.420
Master.

03:04.710 --> 03:05.120
Here.

03:06.080 --> 03:06.940
Uncle Chu Ying.

03:07.840 --> 03:08.960
Such great wine!

03:13.030 --> 03:13.910
Come, Master.

03:14.590 --> 03:15.560
Master, Master.

03:15.840 --> 03:17.040
Come, Uncle Chu Ying.

03:19.710 --> 03:22.120
Xin Xiong,
as a Great Completion Realm cultivator,

03:22.120 --> 03:23.450
rarely meets his match.

03:23.590 --> 03:25.079
Even when he left Tianyuan Sect

03:25.079 --> 03:26.340
to build Xin Xie Manor,

03:26.470 --> 03:27.750
he was able to single-handedly elevate

03:27.750 --> 03:30.630
Xin Xie Manor to the ranks of
the Twelve Immortal Sects.

03:30.630 --> 03:31.490
It's a pity that

03:32.030 --> 03:34.470
there is a decline in talent
and there are no successors.

03:34.470 --> 03:36.150
After guarding this coveted spot
for many years,

03:36.150 --> 03:37.710
only two disciples remain.

03:40.150 --> 03:41.840
They don't even know etiquette.

03:41.840 --> 03:43.280
When they see their elders,

03:43.280 --> 03:45.210
they don't even know to greet them.

03:45.360 --> 03:46.360
No manners at all.

03:50.630 --> 03:53.760
I pay my respects to Senior Uncle
from the Qingshan Sect.

03:55.030 --> 03:56.800
I worry for Xin Xiong.

03:57.190 --> 03:58.790
I wonder if this Xin Xie Manor

03:59.079 --> 04:00.310
will still be able to hold out

04:00.310 --> 04:02.000
after he's gone.

04:03.190 --> 04:05.590
Xin Xie Manor is a quiet,
sparsely populated place.

04:05.590 --> 04:07.630
It's not as lively as the Qingshan Sect.

04:07.630 --> 04:09.310
But my master is healthy

04:09.750 --> 04:11.280
and has the Immortality Pill
to sustain him.

04:11.280 --> 04:13.030
He's not worried about
what happens after he passes away,

04:13.030 --> 04:15.160
so there's no need for you to worry too.

04:15.360 --> 04:16.720
If you have free time in the future,

04:16.720 --> 04:18.160
the Qingshan Sect is always welcome

04:18.160 --> 04:19.490
to come and give advice.

04:23.360 --> 04:24.430
I heard that the Qingshan Sect

04:24.430 --> 04:25.750
is tucked away in a corner

04:25.750 --> 04:26.390
and relies on renting

04:26.390 --> 04:27.480
other sects' land.

04:27.950 --> 04:29.510
It is also the only one among many sects

04:29.510 --> 04:31.190
that doesn't test for immortal perception.

04:31.190 --> 04:32.850
You can join as long as you pay.

04:33.630 --> 04:35.290
Then why didn't you join them?

04:37.480 --> 04:38.340
I have no money.

04:38.560 --> 04:38.960
You...

05:12.070 --> 05:13.870
Bai Zongying from Tianyuan Sect

05:14.240 --> 05:16.900
pays respect to all seniors
and fellow Taoists.

05:19.870 --> 05:21.130
Asking for a scolding.

05:32.070 --> 05:32.870
What's wrong?

05:33.310 --> 05:34.630
You like him?

05:35.190 --> 05:36.159
No, no.

05:37.560 --> 05:38.630
Then who is he?

05:41.480 --> 05:43.270
He's a senior from Tianyuan Sect.

05:43.270 --> 05:44.480
I've seen him a few times,

05:44.480 --> 05:45.740
but he doesn't know me.

05:47.830 --> 05:49.030
You are just into him.

06:00.310 --> 06:00.920
Dr. Zhu.

06:03.160 --> 06:03.820
Taoist Bai.

06:04.870 --> 06:06.830
Is your master not coming this time?

06:06.830 --> 06:07.720
My master is in seclusion.

06:07.720 --> 06:09.120
He ordered me to go ahead.

06:09.210 --> 06:09.800
Once Divine Doctor Su

06:09.800 --> 06:11.120
sets the time for opening the furnace,

06:11.120 --> 06:12.390
our sect's Elder Cang Fengzi

06:12.390 --> 06:14.120
will come in my master's stead.

06:14.870 --> 06:15.310
Okay.

06:22.390 --> 06:23.070
Everyone.

06:24.480 --> 06:25.750
I believe my junior

06:26.190 --> 06:28.270
has already told you the reason

06:28.600 --> 06:30.190
for gathering everyone here.

06:30.190 --> 06:31.950
I will not repeat it.

06:32.680 --> 06:33.750
Now, please

06:34.159 --> 06:35.870
report your respective

06:36.950 --> 06:38.280
Gongshan Jade Tablets.

06:54.630 --> 06:57.030
The Wang family of Jinqiu
has 1 jade tablet.

06:57.430 --> 06:58.680
But my father is old,

06:59.310 --> 07:00.840
and I am also seriously ill.

07:01.120 --> 07:01.750
So,

07:02.720 --> 07:04.750
I would like to request
2 Immortality Pills.

07:04.750 --> 07:06.950
If anyone is willing to
sell their jade tablet,

07:06.950 --> 07:07.810
the Wang family

07:08.190 --> 07:09.870
will not only offer a handsome reward,

07:09.870 --> 07:11.310
but if you have any requests
in the future,

07:11.310 --> 07:13.510
our entire family will also assist you.

07:19.560 --> 07:20.630
The Lingxu Sect originally

07:20.630 --> 07:21.890
only had 1 jade tablet.

07:21.920 --> 07:24.510
But I had a close friend

07:24.920 --> 07:26.160
whose time was running out

07:26.160 --> 07:27.390
and he unfortunately passed away.

07:27.390 --> 07:28.430
But before he died,

07:28.430 --> 07:30.480
he gave me his Gongshan Jade Tablet.

07:31.070 --> 07:31.830
Thus,

07:32.430 --> 07:33.750
I now have 2.

07:35.870 --> 07:37.870
I am a Captain with the Dongyou Army.

07:38.390 --> 07:39.990
I have 1 Gongshan Jade Tablet

07:40.000 --> 07:41.310
and want to exchange it for
an Immortality Pill

07:41.310 --> 07:42.430
for my Lady.

07:45.560 --> 07:47.120
Xin Xie Manor also has one.

07:51.560 --> 07:52.240
Continue.

07:52.560 --> 07:53.420
Sun Moon Cavern

07:54.190 --> 07:55.310
has 5 jade tablets.

07:56.040 --> 07:57.500
Our dynasty has 6 tablets.

07:58.000 --> 07:58.560
Wait.

07:59.190 --> 08:00.290
I remember at first

08:00.560 --> 08:02.600
the imperial family only had 3 tablets.

08:02.600 --> 08:03.800
How did it become 6?

08:04.360 --> 08:05.830
Master Fu is an immortal,

08:06.560 --> 08:07.920
so you might not understand.

08:07.920 --> 08:10.180
There are still many people in this world

08:11.480 --> 08:13.540
who are loyal and love their country.

08:17.040 --> 08:17.900
Qingshan Sect,

08:19.430 --> 08:20.000
1 tablet.

08:21.870 --> 08:23.040
Lingji Mountain,

08:23.800 --> 08:25.000
10 tablets.

08:26.510 --> 08:27.510
That's not right.

08:28.240 --> 08:30.000
Lingji Mountain should have one less than

08:30.000 --> 08:30.930
Sun Moon Cavern.

08:31.500 --> 08:32.960
Why instead of having fewer,

08:32.960 --> 08:34.320
there are actually 6 more?

08:34.320 --> 08:35.750
It could have dropped from the sky,
or we picked up on the road,

08:35.750 --> 08:37.210
or we bought it with money.

08:37.320 --> 08:38.789
It's none of your business.

08:38.789 --> 08:40.190
If you're not convinced,

08:40.190 --> 08:41.919
go buy them with your own money.

08:43.480 --> 08:44.340
Zigai Mountain

08:44.720 --> 08:45.520
has 3 tablets.

08:48.390 --> 08:49.000
Senior.

08:49.390 --> 08:49.960
There...

08:50.550 --> 08:52.080
There are 30 tablets by now.

08:54.460 --> 08:55.990
Are there really that many?

08:58.150 --> 08:59.390
Tianyuan Sect...

09:00.360 --> 09:01.030
20 tablets.

09:02.000 --> 09:02.550
How many?

09:03.390 --> 09:04.320
20 tablets?

09:04.750 --> 09:05.610
Tianyuan Sect,

09:06.150 --> 09:07.000
20 tablets.

09:08.910 --> 09:11.000
You really have the nerve to claim that.

09:11.000 --> 09:12.270
If that's what you're saying,

09:12.270 --> 09:13.600
should I be thanking you

09:14.240 --> 09:15.440
for leaving 10 for me?

09:15.960 --> 09:16.930
Why don't you say

09:16.960 --> 09:18.560
you have 30 tablets instead?

09:18.630 --> 09:19.840
You might as well take them all.

09:19.840 --> 09:20.970
Why did we even come?

09:21.690 --> 09:22.630
Chongling Valley only said

09:22.630 --> 09:24.630
Gongshan Jade Tablets can be
exchanged for the Immortality Pills.

09:24.630 --> 09:26.750
They never said we had to
state their origin.

09:26.750 --> 09:27.390
Tianyuan Sect

09:27.390 --> 09:29.510
will definitely present
these 20 tablets.

09:29.510 --> 09:31.040
If Master Fu has any doubts,

09:31.510 --> 09:32.970
you can come find me later.

09:34.750 --> 09:35.680
Or I can find you,

09:36.750 --> 09:37.550
if you prefer.

09:38.870 --> 09:40.400
T-That won't be necessary.

09:40.550 --> 09:41.630
I was just curious

09:41.960 --> 09:43.090
and asked casually.

09:45.720 --> 09:46.510
Record it.

09:47.200 --> 09:48.000
Tianyuan Sect

09:48.360 --> 09:50.960
has 20 Gongshan Jade Tablets.

09:56.080 --> 09:56.750
Everyone,

09:57.320 --> 09:58.520
that's all for today.

09:59.440 --> 10:02.040
My master still needs time to
refine the pills,

10:02.140 --> 10:04.290
so we cannot yet determine

10:04.320 --> 10:06.670
the exact time for
the Pill-Tasting Conference.

10:06.670 --> 10:08.070
But please rest assured,

10:08.320 --> 10:09.670
it won't take too long.

10:10.200 --> 10:11.270
Today, our valley

10:11.630 --> 10:13.830
has prepared guest rooms for all of you.

10:14.360 --> 10:15.910
You may leave,

10:16.480 --> 10:18.680
or you can stay in the valley for a while.

10:32.200 --> 10:33.750
That's what he said?

10:34.510 --> 10:34.960
No way!

10:35.150 --> 10:37.510
Y-You actually believed him?

10:37.720 --> 10:38.360
I mean...

10:39.550 --> 10:40.460
Let me tell you.

10:40.670 --> 10:42.440
When he was a prince,

10:42.690 --> 10:43.290
I knew

10:43.320 --> 10:44.870
he was no good.

10:46.320 --> 10:47.750
I know him too well.

10:48.360 --> 10:49.670
What nonsense!

10:50.270 --> 10:52.270
You were busy performing back then.

10:52.390 --> 10:54.190
How did you have time to know him?

10:54.960 --> 10:56.000
The palace is

10:56.030 --> 10:57.550
only so big.

10:57.750 --> 10:59.280
What secrets could it hide?

10:59.440 --> 11:00.150
Besides,

11:00.510 --> 11:01.480
at that time,

11:01.910 --> 11:04.200
I was already an eighth-grade musician.

11:05.960 --> 11:07.690
What a high-ranking official!

11:09.220 --> 11:10.810
Don't be so sarcastic,

11:10.840 --> 11:11.360
will you?

11:11.360 --> 11:13.360
Can't you talk properly?

11:17.070 --> 11:18.480
When I was 8 years old,

11:18.510 --> 11:21.080
my parents sold me to the palace.

11:22.750 --> 11:23.840
If it weren't for

11:23.870 --> 11:25.320
my good voice,

11:25.560 --> 11:27.210
I would have been castrated

11:27.240 --> 11:28.510
and sold as a eunuch.

11:29.750 --> 11:31.280
Later, I followed my master

11:31.790 --> 11:33.270
to learn medicine

11:33.630 --> 11:36.320
and built this Chongling Valley.

11:36.960 --> 11:37.750
To be honest,

11:38.270 --> 11:40.630
I've seen a lot

11:42.320 --> 11:43.840
in my life, haven't I?

11:44.650 --> 11:46.050
But I've never seen

11:46.080 --> 11:46.870
anyone so

11:48.200 --> 11:50.080
shameless.

11:51.200 --> 11:54.130
Have you heard the term,
"Master of the Four Realms"?

11:54.390 --> 11:55.590
His honorific title?

11:57.670 --> 11:59.080
He gave it to himself.

11:59.270 --> 12:01.000
He brags about his magnificent

12:01.320 --> 12:02.720
and graceful brushwork.

12:02.840 --> 12:03.500
Guess what?

12:04.320 --> 12:06.000
It's as ugly as it gets.

12:07.390 --> 12:08.250
Let me tell you,

12:08.440 --> 12:10.360
his handwriting is so bad

12:10.720 --> 12:12.780
that I write even better with my foot.

12:16.670 --> 12:17.550
Right.

12:17.870 --> 12:20.750
A-And he also brags about
his painting skills,

12:21.150 --> 12:22.840
saying it can stir up storms

12:23.030 --> 12:24.960
and subdue the spirits.

12:25.320 --> 12:26.450
It's all gibberish!

12:27.390 --> 12:28.150
Right.

12:29.150 --> 12:31.870
Maybe it should be pasted on the door
to guard the house,

12:31.870 --> 12:33.870
or hang it by the bed to ward off evil.

12:35.840 --> 12:39.840
It's disgusting to even look at it.
The living and the dead would shun it.

12:40.870 --> 12:42.630
You don't have to always
compare yourself with him.

12:42.630 --> 12:45.080
I'm not trying to compare.

12:46.270 --> 12:47.960
I just don't understand.

12:48.450 --> 12:48.840
Seriously,

12:48.840 --> 12:50.640
what did you see in him back then?

12:51.120 --> 12:53.720
Why did you insist on taking him
as your disciple?

12:53.720 --> 12:54.120
I mean,

12:54.320 --> 12:56.000
back then, I had begged you for so long,

12:56.000 --> 12:57.440
but you completely ignored me.

12:57.440 --> 13:00.000
You said you'd only take him
as your disciple.

13:00.270 --> 13:01.080
In the end,

13:01.480 --> 13:04.080
I only became an honorary disciple.

13:04.360 --> 13:04.910
This...

13:06.150 --> 13:07.510
It's been so many years.

13:08.200 --> 13:09.460
Why mention him again?

13:10.080 --> 13:11.670
I don't really care.

13:12.440 --> 13:15.120
I just feel it’s a real shame for you.

13:16.320 --> 13:16.920
All right.

13:18.480 --> 13:20.120
You are doing well too, aren't you?

13:20.120 --> 13:21.670
Chongling Valley has been thriving

13:21.670 --> 13:22.800
for all these years.

13:23.120 --> 13:24.510
Even the Twelve Immortal Sects

13:24.510 --> 13:26.370
have to show you some respect too.

13:28.670 --> 13:30.080
Don't mention them to me.

13:30.720 --> 13:32.270
What I despise the most

13:33.120 --> 13:34.630
are those bastards.

13:35.840 --> 13:37.790
It took the human race only

13:38.490 --> 13:41.140
a few thousand years to evolve
from a primitive state

13:41.140 --> 13:43.260
to building their own cities

13:43.550 --> 13:45.600
and developing their own civilization.

13:45.600 --> 13:47.200
In just a few thousand years,

13:47.550 --> 13:49.150
we learned to make paper

13:49.360 --> 13:50.820
and keep written records.

13:51.140 --> 13:52.810
We invented the compass

13:52.840 --> 13:54.960
to navigate the seas.

13:55.390 --> 13:57.480
We know how to manage and think.

13:57.790 --> 13:59.000
We created

13:59.030 --> 14:00.510
a splendid civilization.

14:00.910 --> 14:01.840
But do you know

14:01.870 --> 14:03.480
when

14:04.270 --> 14:06.240
this development stagnated?

14:10.360 --> 14:13.550
It was when cultivation appeared.

14:16.630 --> 14:19.440
The power of a cultivator is limitless,

14:19.550 --> 14:22.150
capable of doing anything.

14:23.240 --> 14:25.200
It was precisely their arrival

14:25.790 --> 14:27.020
that completely destroyed

14:27.020 --> 14:29.080
the progress of human civilization.

14:29.630 --> 14:31.430
You might find it hard to imagine

14:31.600 --> 14:33.080
that it took our species

14:34.600 --> 14:36.170
only a few thousand years to reach

14:36.170 --> 14:37.480
this level of development.

14:37.480 --> 14:40.140
But now, tens of thousands of years
have passed,

14:42.840 --> 14:44.910
and the lives of the commoners

14:47.550 --> 14:48.790
remain the same.

14:49.240 --> 14:51.550
With their faces to the soil
and their backs to the sky,

14:51.550 --> 14:53.750
they practice slash-and-burn farming

14:55.480 --> 14:57.320
and remains at the mercy of the weather.

14:57.320 --> 14:58.960
Be it flood or drought,

14:59.440 --> 15:01.550
as long as a disaster strikes,

15:02.080 --> 15:03.270
the commoners

15:05.270 --> 15:06.600
have no escape.

15:07.630 --> 15:09.120
In today's world,

15:09.150 --> 15:11.880
everyone is committed to
personal cultivation.

15:12.000 --> 15:13.360
Everyone feels that

15:14.120 --> 15:16.320
entering an immortal sect to cultivate

15:16.600 --> 15:18.030
is the best way out.

15:19.000 --> 15:23.080
They constantly delve into alchemy,

15:23.360 --> 15:26.630
breakthroughs, ascension, and immortality.

15:28.670 --> 15:30.600
Under such a trend,

15:31.320 --> 15:32.960
people only focus on

15:33.030 --> 15:34.360
personal cultivation,

15:34.600 --> 15:36.360
and no one cares about

15:37.360 --> 15:39.560
the well-being of the ordinary people.

15:40.320 --> 15:41.080
This way,

15:42.150 --> 15:46.600
the path for the human race
is growing ever narrower.

15:48.550 --> 15:51.080
Then why are you making
the Immortality Pill?

15:51.120 --> 15:54.000
Narrower and narrower...

16:16.600 --> 16:18.270
There are too many people in the valley,

16:18.270 --> 16:19.670
and they refuse to leave.

16:19.910 --> 16:21.770
We don't have enough guest rooms.

16:26.870 --> 16:27.930
Will you stay here?

16:28.390 --> 16:28.840
Yes.

16:30.120 --> 16:31.390
Then you shall stay here.

16:31.390 --> 16:33.360
Where are my two friends?

16:33.510 --> 16:34.570
They are patients.

16:34.720 --> 16:36.180
Patients all stay at Mingzhu House.

16:36.180 --> 16:36.960
If you want to find them,

16:36.960 --> 16:38.220
you can go over and ask.

16:38.240 --> 16:39.120
Okay, got it.

16:39.360 --> 16:41.270
Are you clear about
the rules in the valley?

16:41.270 --> 16:42.030
What rules?

16:43.510 --> 16:45.480
The use of magic is
prohibited in Chongling Valley

16:45.480 --> 16:46.200
Got it.

17:24.400 --> 17:25.960
I'm not done.

17:26.349 --> 17:27.720
Who allowed you to leave?

17:27.720 --> 17:28.780
Then keep talking.

17:30.000 --> 17:30.680
Well,

17:31.520 --> 17:32.640
the room you assigned me

17:32.640 --> 17:33.200
won't do.

17:33.680 --> 17:35.080
There are dense forests
and many birds in this area.

17:35.080 --> 17:36.030
I'm afraid the noise in the morning

17:36.030 --> 17:37.090
will keep me awake.

17:37.640 --> 17:38.440
Change it for me.

17:38.440 --> 17:39.400
I can't.

17:40.480 --> 17:42.140
What kind of attitude is that?

17:42.880 --> 17:44.010
It can't be changed.

17:44.680 --> 17:45.640
You little brat.

17:46.640 --> 17:48.570
I bet you're doing this on purpose!

17:50.940 --> 17:52.590
[Mingzhu House]

18:03.400 --> 18:04.790
This place is so much better

18:04.790 --> 18:06.000
than the room I am in.

18:12.000 --> 18:12.590
We've arranged

18:12.590 --> 18:13.320
with Dr. Zhu.

18:13.550 --> 18:14.400
Tomorrow afternoon,

18:14.400 --> 18:16.110
he will personally examine Miss Lyu.

18:16.110 --> 18:16.970
At the Wei hour,

18:17.000 --> 18:18.330
I'll come to pick you up.

18:18.590 --> 18:19.920
Cunsu Hall is over there.

18:19.920 --> 18:20.780
Meals are free.

18:21.480 --> 18:22.640
If it's inconvenient for you,

18:22.640 --> 18:24.400
you can have someone
deliver the meals to you.

18:24.400 --> 18:24.830
Do you two

18:24.830 --> 18:26.240
have any other questions?

18:26.240 --> 18:26.720
No.

18:27.030 --> 18:27.630
Thank you.

18:28.830 --> 18:29.790
I'll go back now.

18:30.550 --> 18:32.000
Thank you for your trouble.

18:32.000 --> 18:32.600
Take care.

18:32.720 --> 18:33.650
You're welcome.

18:34.200 --> 18:35.860
Take good care of the patient.

18:40.680 --> 18:41.240
Miss Xin.

18:41.790 --> 18:43.050
Where are you staying?

18:43.350 --> 18:44.810
I live near Li Ying Garden.

18:45.680 --> 18:46.270
I know.

18:46.610 --> 18:47.640
I heard all the cultivators

18:47.640 --> 18:48.700
are staying there.

18:50.200 --> 18:51.960
Did you know each other before?

18:54.200 --> 18:55.440
W-We just met.

18:56.350 --> 18:57.270
His name is Huai Qing.

18:57.270 --> 18:58.550
He's Dr. Zhu's disciple.

18:58.550 --> 18:59.410
He's very nice.

19:00.790 --> 19:02.050
He's nice to everyone.

19:02.720 --> 19:03.720
Nice to everyone?

19:03.920 --> 19:04.310
Yes.

19:04.640 --> 19:05.240
Come on in,

19:05.400 --> 19:06.060
have a seat.

19:33.440 --> 19:34.030
Lu.

19:34.860 --> 19:35.430
No.

19:36.200 --> 19:37.200
You go back first.

19:37.400 --> 19:38.200
I need a break.

19:39.790 --> 19:40.720
Xieyun Cottage.

19:41.200 --> 19:42.060
Don't get lost.

19:42.400 --> 19:42.920
Okay.

19:43.960 --> 19:44.440
Okay.

19:58.750 --> 19:59.810
Why am I here again?

20:00.350 --> 20:02.080
Wasn't I just here a moment ago?

20:13.640 --> 20:14.270
Senior.

20:14.680 --> 20:15.480
Senior!

20:16.030 --> 20:17.330
How do we get to the pantry

20:17.330 --> 20:18.330
at Li Ying Garden?

20:24.380 --> 20:28.320
♪ Honor and disgrace;
rumors and prejudice ♪

20:29.110 --> 20:32.510
♪ Everyone has their own take ♪

20:33.150 --> 20:36.970
♪ Fingers coated in blood
and disasters brought about ♪

20:37.000 --> 20:40.230
♪ Were never what I wanted ♪

20:40.520 --> 20:44.360
♪ The great way is fading away,
besieged by mysterious traps ♪

20:45.230 --> 20:48.980
♪ Who dares to treat life and death
as nothing? ♪

20:49.010 --> 20:52.730
♪ In the blink of an eye, the body
collapses, and the soul is destroyed ♪

20:52.750 --> 20:57.730
♪ The fire starts raging across the land ♪

20:57.050 --> 20:58.400
Senior, are you also here for

20:58.400 --> 21:00.130
the Pill-Tasting Conference?

21:01.400 --> 21:02.730
I'm a friend of Su Taiyi.

21:03.820 --> 21:05.750
You are Divine Doctor Su's friend.

21:05.880 --> 21:07.540
Then I should call you Senior.

21:09.270 --> 21:10.510
I'm Xin Mei from Xin Xie Manor.

21:10.510 --> 21:12.110
May I know your name, Senior?

21:13.270 --> 21:14.000
Lu Qianqiao.

21:14.680 --> 21:17.340
"Qian" as in one in a thousand,
"qiao" as in tree.

21:17.640 --> 21:19.400
So you are Mr. Lu.

21:21.480 --> 21:22.550
I recognize this place now.

21:22.550 --> 21:24.080
You don't need to see me off.

21:26.200 --> 21:27.200
Thank you, Mr. Lu.

21:27.440 --> 21:28.700
I'll take my leave now.

21:43.000 --> 21:45.920
What a small world.

21:49.680 --> 21:50.940
Sobered up so quickly?

21:52.070 --> 21:53.310
Guess who I just saw.

21:55.400 --> 21:56.860
Was it Xiaotao, Xiaohong,

21:56.880 --> 21:58.880
or Chunxing, Qiuju?

21:59.640 --> 22:00.370
None of them.

22:00.640 --> 22:02.500
It's Miss Xiahua from Wei County.

22:02.960 --> 22:04.750
The one who beat the drum in Wei County

22:04.750 --> 22:06.420
to seek justice for her father.

22:06.420 --> 22:07.400
It was you, Lord Lu Huai,

22:07.400 --> 22:08.400
who presided over the case.

22:08.400 --> 22:10.060
I was the one who picked her up.

22:12.000 --> 22:13.640
From the office's entrance to the hall,

22:13.640 --> 22:15.170
it's only a few dozen steps.

22:15.200 --> 22:17.000
You actually managed to hook her up?

22:17.000 --> 22:18.270
What do you mean by "hook up"?

22:18.270 --> 22:19.830
Our relationship is pure

22:20.000 --> 22:21.070
and innocent.

22:22.480 --> 22:24.590
She's recuperating
in Chongling Valley now,

22:24.590 --> 22:26.030
staying in Mingzhu House.

22:26.030 --> 22:27.440
I'll go accompany her for a few days.

22:27.440 --> 22:28.160
Coincidentally,

22:28.160 --> 22:29.620
you also met Immortal Xin.

22:29.960 --> 22:31.000
You should try harder,

22:31.000 --> 22:33.260
and maybe you can rekindle your romance.

22:34.830 --> 22:35.760
Have a good time.

22:42.790 --> 22:43.830
Wait for me!

22:43.880 --> 22:44.590
Hurry up!

22:45.110 --> 22:45.880
Coming!

22:46.680 --> 22:47.540
Is it like this?

22:48.240 --> 22:48.960
Add a sword!

22:49.680 --> 22:50.480
Right, right.

22:50.550 --> 22:51.350
Make the face thinner.

22:51.350 --> 22:52.280
Make it thinner.

22:52.410 --> 22:53.240
Draw it well for me.

22:53.240 --> 22:53.570
Okay.

22:55.790 --> 22:56.670
And here.

23:02.480 --> 23:04.400
Have you seen the woman in this painting?

23:04.400 --> 23:06.060
You know this crazy woman too?

23:06.510 --> 23:07.310
I was at home,

23:07.510 --> 23:08.600
teaching my wife a lesson,

23:08.600 --> 23:09.440
when she rushed in and

23:09.440 --> 23:10.240
beat me up.

23:10.640 --> 23:12.240
Look, she loosened my teeth.

23:12.590 --> 23:14.110
Then she just turned and left,

23:14.110 --> 23:15.510
without even giving me half a coin.

23:15.510 --> 23:16.640
Which way did she go?

23:17.790 --> 23:18.320
That way.

23:18.720 --> 23:20.320
What, did she beat you up too?

23:23.160 --> 23:23.680
Miss.

23:27.160 --> 23:28.350
Do you think it's her?

23:28.350 --> 23:29.080
I don't know.

23:29.400 --> 23:30.360
We'll just do whatever

23:30.360 --> 23:31.560
our benefactor says.

23:31.720 --> 23:33.180
Where else can we find a job

23:33.240 --> 23:34.700
this easy and profitable?

23:57.590 --> 23:58.720
Is there a customer?

23:58.720 --> 23:59.380
Have a seat.

24:02.550 --> 24:03.440
It's hot today,

24:03.590 --> 24:04.850
and it's right at noon.

24:04.940 --> 24:06.670
I see you've had a long journey.

24:06.720 --> 24:07.980
You must be exhausted.

24:08.310 --> 24:09.830
How about a bowl of barley tea?

24:09.830 --> 24:12.240
It's the best way to quench your thirst
and cool off.

24:12.240 --> 24:13.640
Have you seen this woman?

24:15.960 --> 24:16.720
No.

24:21.880 --> 24:22.680
Just kidding.

24:23.640 --> 24:24.570
You've seen her?

24:24.720 --> 24:25.960
When? Where is she?

24:26.830 --> 24:28.110
This is a teahouse

24:28.270 --> 24:29.930
where people can come to rest.

24:30.200 --> 24:31.550
You came in and started questioning,

24:31.550 --> 24:32.270
like an official

24:32.270 --> 24:33.440
interrogating a prisoner.

24:33.440 --> 24:35.030
You didn't even order a pot of tea.

24:35.030 --> 24:36.630
How am I supposed to host you?

24:41.270 --> 24:42.400
Bring me a pot of tea.

24:43.440 --> 24:44.890
Although herbal tea quenches thirst,

24:44.890 --> 24:45.720
asking for information

24:45.720 --> 24:46.680
is tiring.

24:47.270 --> 24:49.130
You must order a pot of Biluochun.

24:57.440 --> 24:58.500
Is this Biluochun?

24:58.830 --> 24:59.480
Yes.

24:59.790 --> 25:00.880
Our exclusive recipe.

25:00.880 --> 25:03.110
Naturally, it's different from elsewhere.

25:03.110 --> 25:03.920
Please enjoy.

25:05.680 --> 25:06.680
I ordered the tea,

25:06.920 --> 25:08.050
and paid the silver.

25:08.240 --> 25:10.440
You can tell me the truth now, can't you?

25:10.750 --> 25:12.880
Well, I’ll have to give that some thought.

25:12.880 --> 25:14.750
Our teahouse is a hub for travelers.

25:14.750 --> 25:16.810
There are many people who come and go.

25:17.260 --> 25:18.400
Many just have a sip of tea,

25:18.400 --> 25:19.720
rest their feet, and then leave.

25:19.720 --> 25:20.960
There are so many faces,

25:20.960 --> 25:22.790
so I have to recall carefully.

25:26.440 --> 25:28.100
Then bring another pot of tea.

25:30.550 --> 25:31.480
Thank you, Miss.

25:33.750 --> 25:35.480
That woman is slender

25:36.000 --> 25:37.860
and is about the same height as me.

25:37.960 --> 25:39.490
She has delicate features,

25:39.750 --> 25:40.880
a gentle voice,

25:41.480 --> 25:43.410
yet possesses a certain tenacity.

25:44.270 --> 25:45.600
She loves to use a sword.

25:45.720 --> 25:46.980
That sword is special.

25:47.110 --> 25:49.310
It looks like a crescent moon
and is very pretty.

25:49.310 --> 25:50.200
I think...

25:51.200 --> 25:53.200
if that sword were to take your life,

25:53.720 --> 25:55.590
it should be quite easy.

25:56.480 --> 25:57.410
What did you say?

26:15.880 --> 26:16.680
Grandmaster.

26:17.340 --> 26:18.240
I, as the Master,

26:18.240 --> 26:19.790
have everything prepared.

26:20.370 --> 26:21.630
When the time is right,

26:22.070 --> 26:24.110
I will renew your bones for you,
Grandmaster.

26:24.110 --> 26:24.880
I've already prepared

26:24.880 --> 26:26.080
a set of animal bones.

26:26.270 --> 26:28.270
It's being nourished in the cold spring
in the back mountain.

26:28.270 --> 26:29.270
Animal bones?

26:30.070 --> 26:31.030
Animal bones...

26:31.280 --> 26:31.930
might be

26:31.960 --> 26:33.750
the closest thing to human bones,

26:33.750 --> 26:36.000
they afterall are not of the same origin.

26:36.000 --> 26:37.220
They simply cannot merge

26:37.220 --> 26:38.750
with human flesh and blood.

26:38.920 --> 26:41.250
I'm afraid it will cause other illnesses.

26:41.270 --> 26:43.360
For example, weak constitution,
a body that easily feels cold,

26:43.360 --> 26:44.200
and severe heartache.

26:44.200 --> 26:44.800
It's okay.

26:45.160 --> 26:45.720
I know.

26:46.270 --> 26:47.410
Then why would you still, Grandmaster...

26:47.410 --> 26:48.890
If I don't use animal bones,

26:48.890 --> 26:49.880
should I go find a set of

26:49.880 --> 26:51.030
actual human bones?

26:51.750 --> 26:52.550
Rest assured.

26:52.920 --> 26:54.120
I know what I'm doing.

26:57.400 --> 26:57.860
Dr. Zhu.

26:58.680 --> 26:59.140
Dr. Zhu!

26:59.550 --> 27:01.010
Acute cough and wheezing!

27:01.110 --> 27:02.070
Coming!

27:04.440 --> 27:05.000
Master!

27:06.590 --> 27:08.320
Master, you dropped your shoe!

27:36.440 --> 27:37.370
Feeling better?

27:39.110 --> 27:40.030
Much better.

27:40.680 --> 27:42.110
Thank you, Dr. Zhu.

27:43.400 --> 27:44.110
No problem.

27:44.790 --> 27:46.310
Just rest well.

27:46.440 --> 27:47.000
Okay.

27:49.670 --> 27:51.780
[Shunxin Residence]

27:58.070 --> 27:59.550
These are fruit sent by Chongling Valley?

27:59.550 --> 28:00.030
Yes.

28:00.200 --> 28:01.400
This is all they have.

28:06.110 --> 28:07.720
I really can't live like this anymore.

28:07.720 --> 28:08.270
Young Sect Master,

28:07.990 --> 28:10.660
[Xu Feng from Lingji Mountain]

28:08.480 --> 28:09.920
the Immortality Pill
is about to be unsealed.

28:09.920 --> 28:11.480
We will soon return to the sect.

28:11.480 --> 28:12.960
1 Gongshan Jade Tablet

28:13.070 --> 28:15.000
exchanges for 1 Immortality Pill.

28:15.350 --> 28:17.330
The Tianyuan Sect reported 20 tokens.

28:17.330 --> 28:18.400
With the 10 tablets I reported,

28:18.400 --> 28:19.660
that makes 30 tablets.

28:20.440 --> 28:22.170
Exactly enough to distribute.

28:22.680 --> 28:23.620
Young Sect Master,

28:23.620 --> 28:25.110
Sun Moon Cavern's capabilities
shouldn't be underestimated.

28:25.110 --> 28:26.240
They have 5 tablets.

28:27.110 --> 28:28.510
On this train of thought,

28:28.640 --> 28:30.570
the imperial family has 6 tablets,

28:32.880 --> 28:34.640
while Bai Zongying has 9 tablets left.

28:34.640 --> 28:35.920
Do you think they have 、
enough to distribute?

28:35.920 --> 28:36.980
Young Sect Master,

28:37.070 --> 28:38.530
don't worry about others.

28:38.790 --> 28:39.640
The Sect Master has made it clear.

28:39.640 --> 28:40.290
This time,

28:40.350 --> 28:42.030
he asked you to exchange
those 4 jade tablets,

28:42.030 --> 28:43.760
but you reported 10 all at once.

28:47.440 --> 28:49.300
Tianyuan Sect only has 5 tablets,

28:49.590 --> 28:51.590
but Bai Zongying dared to report 20.

28:51.830 --> 28:53.200
If I reported anything less,

28:53.200 --> 28:54.070
wouldn't it be an embarrassment

28:54.070 --> 28:54.880
for our Lingji Mountain?

28:54.880 --> 28:55.350
Then...

28:56.240 --> 28:58.300
What are we going to do about the rest?

28:58.350 --> 28:58.750
Look.

29:00.030 --> 29:00.760
What is this?

29:02.070 --> 29:02.730
Bank notes?

29:03.280 --> 29:03.960
This land in Zigai Mountain,

29:03.960 --> 29:05.420
owned by Cai En, is leased.

29:05.830 --> 29:07.430
The lease is about to expire.

29:07.450 --> 29:08.590
They haven't renewed the lease,

29:08.590 --> 29:09.920
nor have they moved out.

29:09.960 --> 29:11.290
Why do you think that is?

29:11.590 --> 29:12.450
Think about it.

29:12.830 --> 29:13.830
Those two mortals

29:13.830 --> 29:15.270
were dressed in rags.

29:15.960 --> 29:16.960
I have no idea where

29:16.960 --> 29:18.360
they got that jade token.

29:18.510 --> 29:18.970
Xu Feng.

29:19.310 --> 29:20.110
Let me ask you,

29:20.680 --> 29:22.830
why do people want to live forever?

29:23.400 --> 29:24.110
Why?

29:24.270 --> 29:26.530
For a carefree and happy life, of course.

29:27.070 --> 29:28.530
Even if they live forever,

29:29.110 --> 29:30.310
can they be carefree?

29:30.440 --> 29:32.570
You're brilliant, Young Sect Master.

29:33.200 --> 29:34.800
But this is still not enough.

29:36.000 --> 29:37.000
I have my ways.

29:38.160 --> 29:38.640
Go.

29:39.160 --> 29:40.090
Give this letter

29:40.200 --> 29:41.240
to that female disciple

29:41.240 --> 29:42.200
from Xin Xie Manor.

29:42.200 --> 29:42.880
Tell her

29:43.310 --> 29:44.510
that I'll be waiting for her

29:44.510 --> 29:45.790
right here.

30:12.830 --> 30:13.400
May I ask,

30:13.830 --> 30:16.230
are you Immortal Xin Mei
from Xin Xie Manor?

30:16.480 --> 30:17.200
Who are you?

30:17.480 --> 30:19.680
Our Young Sect Master would like to
have a word with you.

30:19.680 --> 30:20.480
Immortal Xin,

30:20.830 --> 30:22.310
would it be convenient for you to go to
Shunxin Residence for a chat?

30:22.310 --> 30:23.240
It's not convenient.

30:23.240 --> 30:23.960
I'm not feeling well today.

30:23.960 --> 30:25.160
Then when will you have time?

30:25.160 --> 30:26.160
Our Young Sect Master

30:26.160 --> 30:27.560
is from Lingji Mountain—

30:28.200 --> 30:29.660
He's even waiting for you!

30:32.790 --> 30:33.350
Auntie,

30:33.480 --> 30:34.510
do you want a queue number?

30:34.510 --> 30:36.040
It's a dozen numbers earlier than this.

30:36.040 --> 30:36.680
Two taels of silver

30:36.680 --> 30:37.510
for one.

30:37.830 --> 30:39.200
I'll take it.

30:39.400 --> 30:40.110
Alright.

30:40.400 --> 30:41.060
Here you go.

30:41.350 --> 30:42.110
Go inside.

30:46.960 --> 30:47.640
Miss Xin?

30:49.270 --> 30:50.070
Miss Xin!

30:52.030 --> 30:53.440
It's you, Zhang Dahu.

30:53.510 --> 30:54.110
Yes.

30:54.920 --> 30:56.980
Are you here to see a doctor, Miss Xin?

30:57.310 --> 30:58.310
Not feeling well?

30:58.680 --> 30:59.610
Tell me about it.

30:59.960 --> 31:00.440
I have been

31:00.440 --> 31:01.880
walking through this valley for years.

31:01.880 --> 31:03.610
I'm practically half a doctor.

31:04.680 --> 31:06.610
I just can't drink water recently.

31:06.920 --> 31:08.780
I throw up as soon as I drink water.

31:09.440 --> 31:10.960
Then you can't line up here.

31:10.960 --> 31:12.360
This is Dr. Zhu's clinic.

31:12.510 --> 31:14.480
He specializes in colds, emphysema,

31:14.480 --> 31:15.790
and heart and chest diseases.

31:15.790 --> 31:17.640
You seem to be having
some digestive issues.

31:17.640 --> 31:18.900
You should see Dr. Liu.

31:19.030 --> 31:20.080
He's good at treating your sort of issues.

31:20.080 --> 31:21.000
I'll take you there.

31:21.000 --> 31:21.680
Dr. Liu?

31:22.160 --> 31:23.200
Yes, Dr. Liu.

31:23.270 --> 31:23.960
Just right ahead.

31:23.960 --> 31:24.960
Let's go that way.

31:25.200 --> 31:25.730
Let's go.

31:26.680 --> 31:27.340
Senior Liu.

31:27.920 --> 31:28.980
You're here again.

31:29.590 --> 31:31.650
Delivering a letter to Senior Zhang.

31:35.270 --> 31:35.920
Come here.

31:36.240 --> 31:36.920
Right here.

31:38.880 --> 31:39.680
Dr. Liu

31:39.870 --> 31:41.310
specializes in regulating
the spleen and stomach.

31:41.310 --> 31:42.310
But he as he gets older,

31:42.310 --> 31:43.790
he only does rounds on the 7th and 9th

31:43.790 --> 31:44.590
of each month.

31:45.680 --> 31:46.340
Isn't today

31:46.750 --> 31:47.720
the 7th?

31:48.550 --> 31:49.440
His queue numbers

31:49.440 --> 31:51.170
were snapped up two months ago.

31:52.640 --> 31:53.370
Don't worry.

31:53.680 --> 31:55.010
I have a way to get you in.

31:55.240 --> 31:55.830
Get in?

31:56.480 --> 31:57.240
How?

31:58.030 --> 31:59.440
Your illness came suddenly.

31:59.440 --> 32:00.790
We have to make an exception.

32:00.790 --> 32:01.550
Here's the plan.

32:01.550 --> 32:02.070
In a bit,

32:02.350 --> 32:03.200
step on my shoulders

32:03.200 --> 32:04.930
and we'll climb over from here.

32:06.550 --> 32:07.310
Don't worry.

32:07.640 --> 32:08.310
In our Chongling Valley,

32:08.310 --> 32:09.680
the use of magic is forbidden.

32:09.680 --> 32:11.610
I don't need magic for this height.

32:15.830 --> 32:16.890
She flew that high?

32:22.440 --> 32:22.970
Let's go!

32:30.350 --> 32:30.880
Miss Xin.

32:31.790 --> 32:32.920
Stop walking.

32:33.030 --> 32:34.030
This is the place.

32:35.270 --> 32:36.330
In a moment, Dr. Liu

32:36.640 --> 32:37.550
will come out of there.

32:37.550 --> 32:38.440
As soon as he comes out,

32:38.440 --> 32:39.170
you rush over

32:39.440 --> 32:40.550
and lie on the ground.

32:40.550 --> 32:41.720
Don't worry. Trust me.

32:41.720 --> 32:43.450
No doctor will just ignore you.

32:44.480 --> 32:45.390
What's with the "ah"?

32:45.390 --> 32:47.000
Are you afraid of looking foolish
just to get treated?

32:47.000 --> 32:48.920
Do you want your life or your pride?

32:48.920 --> 32:49.550
But...

32:50.030 --> 32:51.590
It's just that getting an appointment
with Dr. Liu

32:51.590 --> 32:52.190
is so hard.

32:52.680 --> 32:55.610
By the time it's your turn,
you might already be dead.

32:55.680 --> 32:57.010
Listen to me. Follow me.

33:17.310 --> 33:17.830
Oh no.

33:18.350 --> 33:19.350
My stomach hurts.

33:20.550 --> 33:21.310
Maybe I ate something bad

33:21.310 --> 33:22.160
last night.

33:22.920 --> 33:23.830
I need to go to the toilet.

33:23.830 --> 33:24.610
I'll be right back.

33:24.610 --> 33:25.140
Don't go.

33:25.720 --> 33:27.400
What am I supposed to do without you?

33:27.400 --> 33:28.070
My lady.

33:28.590 --> 33:30.050
Didn't I tell you already?

33:30.310 --> 33:31.570
As soon as he comes out,

33:31.680 --> 33:33.940
just lie on the ground and scream in pain.

33:34.170 --> 33:35.200
The physicians in our valley

33:35.200 --> 33:36.200
all have a heart of gold.

33:36.200 --> 33:37.460
They won't ignore you.

33:38.310 --> 33:39.640
Be sure not to hesitate.

33:59.000 --> 34:00.480
Why am I sweating so much?

34:20.440 --> 34:21.070
Mr. Lu.

35:06.030 --> 35:07.760
Master, slow down.

35:08.000 --> 35:09.130
Wait for me, Master!

35:13.380 --> 35:14.610
Master, your shoes.

35:14.960 --> 35:16.800
Master, your shoes!

35:17.590 --> 35:18.190
Master!

35:18.320 --> 35:19.520
Master, your shoes.

35:19.550 --> 35:20.670
Master!

35:20.840 --> 35:22.030
I heard you brought a patient back.

35:22.030 --> 35:23.760
Where is she? Let me take a look.

35:24.030 --> 35:25.570
I taught you all your medical skills.

35:25.570 --> 35:27.230
What are you hoping to look at?

35:27.280 --> 35:29.400
All the more I must take a look.

35:29.710 --> 35:30.880
I want to see what kind of patient

35:30.880 --> 35:31.570
could receive

35:31.570 --> 35:33.090
personal treatment from

35:33.440 --> 35:34.960
of the Grandmaster of Chongling Valley.

35:34.960 --> 35:36.150
Master, your shoes.

35:41.760 --> 35:42.360
By the way,

35:43.510 --> 35:45.400
you're sure she's a young woman,

35:45.480 --> 35:45.960
right?

35:57.190 --> 35:58.450
Grandmaster, please.

36:05.030 --> 36:08.290
There's just something about
this girl that I really like.

36:08.760 --> 36:09.630
How old is she?

36:10.960 --> 36:11.840
About your age.

36:13.840 --> 36:14.640
A cultivator?

36:16.160 --> 36:18.230
She looks like
such a sweet, delicate girl.

36:18.230 --> 36:19.070
I thought...

36:19.630 --> 36:21.830
you liked the bright and charming type.

36:22.150 --> 36:23.410
Will you still see her?

36:23.710 --> 36:24.760
Yes.

36:44.960 --> 36:46.030
Spell of Utterance.

36:46.030 --> 36:46.440
Yes.

36:48.760 --> 36:49.320
Master.

36:49.920 --> 36:51.650
What is the Spell of Utterance?

36:55.370 --> 36:56.630
The Spell of Utterance is a kind of magic

36:56.630 --> 36:58.630
where whatever you say becomes law.

36:58.670 --> 37:00.710
No matter how unreasonable the request is,

37:00.710 --> 37:01.320
the one under the spell

37:01.320 --> 37:04.380
will follow all instructions
to complete the request.

37:04.770 --> 37:06.560
It reminds me of the cold case

37:06.590 --> 37:07.640
that shocked the Yong region back then.

37:07.640 --> 37:08.710
It was a young, wealthy man who was

37:08.710 --> 37:10.030
under influence of the spell.

37:10.030 --> 37:11.880
In broad daylight,

37:12.280 --> 37:13.550
he slit his own throat.

37:14.550 --> 37:16.000
It's said that this kind of magic

37:16.000 --> 37:17.600
has been lost for many years.

37:18.360 --> 37:19.220
I didn't expect

37:20.480 --> 37:21.680
to see it again today.

37:22.480 --> 37:24.630
But this sort of magic
is extremely powerful

37:24.630 --> 37:26.160
and has many restrictions.

37:27.710 --> 37:28.400
First,

37:29.300 --> 37:31.280
the spellcaster's cultivation level

37:31.280 --> 37:33.410
must be much higher than the victim's.

37:33.550 --> 37:34.150
Second,

37:34.370 --> 37:36.110
it's easier to take effect when the victim

37:36.110 --> 37:37.510
is completely off guard.

37:38.120 --> 37:39.850
The only way to break it is to

37:39.920 --> 37:41.980
kill the person who casted the spell.

37:43.340 --> 37:45.150
But she is still in the
Foundation Establishment Stage.

37:45.150 --> 37:46.920
Looking at the whole Chongling Valley,

37:46.920 --> 37:48.880
there are many whose cultivation
is higher than hers.

37:48.880 --> 37:49.800
If this spell

37:49.960 --> 37:51.360
was not cast in the valley

37:51.590 --> 37:52.880
but on the way here,

37:54.000 --> 37:56.200
it will be hard to find who was behind it.

37:56.840 --> 37:57.630
So what exactly are

37:57.630 --> 37:59.320
her symptoms now?

38:00.710 --> 38:02.840
A large amount of water is
seeping out of her body.

38:02.840 --> 38:04.240
I tried to feed her water,

38:04.480 --> 38:06.140
but it worsened the symptoms.

38:07.880 --> 38:09.070
So it seems,

38:10.000 --> 38:11.800
before we find the spellcaster,

38:13.000 --> 38:14.730
we still have to feed her water.

38:15.800 --> 38:17.260
Fish Drinking Technique.

38:18.800 --> 38:19.860
You taught me that.

38:37.400 --> 38:38.260
Is anyone here?

38:40.550 --> 38:41.410
Is anyone here?

39:51.150 --> 39:52.360
I didn't expect

39:52.550 --> 39:53.880
to meet you here, Mr. Lu.

39:55.070 --> 39:56.100
I was actually going

39:56.100 --> 39:57.350
to see Dr. Zhu Yu.

39:58.230 --> 39:59.800
But the line was too long.

40:00.190 --> 40:01.230
Then a guy

40:01.230 --> 40:02.960
who knows Chongling Valley well

40:02.960 --> 40:03.800
brought me to

40:03.800 --> 40:05.070
the backyard of Suwen Hall.

40:05.070 --> 40:06.190
He said I could wait there

40:06.190 --> 40:07.400
for Dr. Liu, who specializes in

40:07.400 --> 40:08.710
the spleen and stomach.

40:08.710 --> 40:09.480
And then...

40:09.670 --> 40:11.480
And then you had to lay on the ground

40:11.480 --> 40:13.280
to get the doctor to examine you.

40:16.480 --> 40:17.630
Many people do this.

40:18.030 --> 40:19.230
You are not the first.

40:22.590 --> 40:23.590
Give me your hand.

40:25.480 --> 40:26.810
Let me check your pulse.

40:36.510 --> 40:38.440
Mr. Lu, you also know medicine?

40:39.510 --> 40:40.110
A little.

40:46.230 --> 40:47.890
Your condition is stable now.

40:48.070 --> 40:48.760
But until we find

40:48.760 --> 40:50.400
a permanent solution,

40:50.630 --> 40:52.280
you can't drink any more water.

40:52.280 --> 40:53.810
Can't drink any more water?

40:54.070 --> 40:54.630
Mr. Lu,

40:55.230 --> 40:56.890
what exactly is wrong with me?

40:57.320 --> 40:58.360
It's not an illness.

40:58.360 --> 40:59.090
It's a spell,

40:59.360 --> 41:00.590
called the Spell of Utterance.

41:00.590 --> 41:01.760
Spell of Utterance?

41:02.550 --> 41:05.480
You can understand it as
absolute obedience to the spoken word.

41:05.480 --> 41:06.840
Once this spell is cast,

41:07.110 --> 41:09.040
the victim will follow every order

41:09.110 --> 41:10.240
of the spellcaster.

41:10.800 --> 41:11.800
Think carefully.

41:12.440 --> 41:13.440
When did your body

41:13.590 --> 41:14.400
first start

41:14.440 --> 41:15.440
having problems?

41:16.320 --> 41:17.710
If you put it that way,

41:18.710 --> 41:21.190
it must have been in Pingxiang Town.

41:21.960 --> 41:23.490
I was just passing through,

41:23.630 --> 41:25.030
and then a

41:25.030 --> 41:26.190
crazy man

41:26.440 --> 41:27.280
ran toward me.

41:27.840 --> 41:29.370
Judging by his appearance,

41:29.550 --> 41:30.800
he didn't look like he was
from the Central Plains.

41:30.800 --> 41:32.230
He looked like he was from North Xiang.

41:32.230 --> 41:33.550
He told me

41:33.630 --> 41:34.880
the water was poisoned

41:34.880 --> 41:36.190
and told me not to drink it.

41:36.190 --> 41:36.800
At the time, I thought

41:36.800 --> 41:38.060
I had just met a madman.

41:38.280 --> 41:39.410
Thinking back on it,

41:40.230 --> 41:42.090
I haven't been able to drink water

41:42.190 --> 41:43.070
since then.

41:46.070 --> 41:47.360
But I’ve done nothing

41:47.440 --> 41:48.640
against this madman.

41:48.710 --> 41:50.240
Why would he want to harm me?

41:50.710 --> 41:52.510
He might not be the spellcaster.

41:52.800 --> 41:54.440
When casting the Spell of Utterance,

41:54.440 --> 41:55.360
sometimes

41:55.360 --> 41:56.800
the spellcaster doesn't need
to be present.

41:56.800 --> 41:57.880
People, animals,

41:58.480 --> 41:59.480
even a green leaf

41:59.880 --> 42:01.810
can serve as a medium for the spell.

42:03.030 --> 42:03.760
I didn't notice it

42:03.760 --> 42:05.030
at all back then.

42:06.230 --> 42:07.230
The Spell of Utterance

42:07.230 --> 42:08.480
can only be cast by
a higher-level cultivator

42:08.480 --> 42:09.710
on a lower-level one.

42:10.110 --> 42:11.310
Your powers are weak.

42:11.480 --> 42:13.210
It's normal you didn't feel it.

42:14.920 --> 42:16.320
How can I break the spell?

42:16.550 --> 42:17.950
Please advise me, Mr. Lu.

42:19.150 --> 42:20.410
Kill the spellcaster.

42:21.760 --> 42:22.890
Is that the only way?

42:22.960 --> 42:24.090
That's the only way.

42:26.000 --> 42:26.960
Then I'm doomed.

42:27.070 --> 42:28.320
I... I can't even imagine

42:28.320 --> 42:29.720
who would want to harm me.

42:29.880 --> 42:30.400
And

42:30.710 --> 42:32.510
if I can't find the spellcaster,

42:32.960 --> 42:35.290
does it mean I can never
drink water again?

42:36.550 --> 42:38.480
Since you consider me your senior,

42:38.630 --> 42:39.920
I won't let you die.

42:41.400 --> 42:42.730
Do you have a way, Mr. Lu?

42:42.840 --> 42:43.230
Yes.

42:50.320 --> 42:50.880
Mr. Lu,

42:51.070 --> 42:52.130
where are we going?

42:53.230 --> 42:53.920
Qiyue Lake.

42:54.780 --> 42:56.150
The Qiyue Lake in Chongling Valley

42:56.150 --> 42:57.150
has crystal clear water

42:57.150 --> 42:58.360
and extremely dense spiritual energy.

42:58.360 --> 42:59.560
It's extraordinary.

42:59.960 --> 43:00.760
The spiritual plants here

43:00.760 --> 43:01.670
grow very well

43:02.070 --> 43:03.880
because they are watered by the pool.
